longBusinessSummary: Globe Net Wireless Corp. develops an open source application programming interface ecosystem and provides internet for rural communities. It develops TextPro Connect and BizPro utility service apps for the mobile business market. The company was founded in 2009 and is headquartered in Hong Kong, Hong Kong.
